#  Library Management System -- Console app


##  Key Features

- Inventory Management: Add, remove, and list books with real-time stock tracking.
- Search: Find books instantly by their unique ID.
- Lending System: - Automated stock reduction upon loaning.
 - Automatic availability status updates (sets to 'unavailable' when stock hits 0).
- Data Persistence: Automatically saves all changes to a `books.json` file using the Google GSON library.
-  Error Handling: Custom exceptions ensure that books cannot be added without a title, author, or ID.


##  Installation & Usage

1. Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/ivanyoslaszlo/bookHandler.git

2. Run the Main.java class from your favorite IDE (IntelliJ, Eclipse, or VS Code).


